snippet.title: Insurgence - Second Assault PV
snippet.description:
Insurgence - Second Assault is a follow-up sequel to Chains of Renegade. Which takes the point of view from different characters and factions.

Wishlist us on steam! [https://store.steampowered.com/app/1081100/Insurgence__Second_Assault/]

Music
Words / Vocal: Fuuka Mariwo 
Music: Sakagami Souichi ( http://www.tandess.com/en/music/ )
